request.description:
This endpoint allows users to sign up by creating a new account. The request should be sent as an HTTP POST to the specified URL. The request body should contain the following parameters in JSON format:

- `username` (string): The username of the new user.
    
- `email` (string): The email address of the new user.
    
- `password` (string): The password for the new account.
    
- `country` (string): The country of residence for the new user.
    
- `browserName` (string): The name of the browser used for signing up.
    
- `deviceType` (string): The type of device used for signing up.
    
- `profilePicture` (string): The profile picture of the new user in base64 format.
    

Upon successful execution, the response will contain the relevant information for the newly created user account.
